## Sequence Diagrams ##

### Initial Page Load ###

img/SEQ_Initial_Page_Load.png

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Visitor
    participant Browser
    participant HTML as index.html
    participant CSS as styles.css
    participant JS as script.js

    Visitor->>Browser: Open website
    Browser->>HTML: Request page
    HTML-->>Browser: Return static markup
    Browser->>CSS: Load stylesheet
    CSS-->>Browser: Return styles
    Browser->>JS: Load script
    JS-->>Browser: Return behavior script
    Browser->>Browser: Render profile sections
    Browser->>Browser: Initialize menu, reveal, and navigation behavior
    Browser-->>Visitor: Display website
```

### Mobile Navigation ###

img/SEQ_Mobile Navigation.png

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Visitor
    participant UI as Website UI
    participant JS as script.js
    participant Section as Target Section

    Visitor->>UI: Tap menu button
    UI->>JS: Trigger menu toggle
    JS-->>UI: Show mobile navigation
    Visitor->>UI: Select section link
    UI->>JS: Trigger navigation handler
    JS->>Section: Scroll to selected section
    JS-->>UI: Close mobile navigation
    UI-->>Visitor: Display selected section
```

### Guided Career Journey ###

img/SEQ_Guided_Career_Journey.png

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Visitor
    participant Home
    participant About
    participant Notes
    participant Timeline
    participant Experience
    participant Domains
    participant Background
    participant Contact

    Visitor->>Home: Read role and positioning
    Visitor->>About: Understand working style
    Visitor->>Notes: Review professional principles
    Visitor->>Timeline: Scan career stages
    Visitor->>Experience: Validate detailed job evidence
    Visitor->>Domains: Review business exposure
    Visitor->>Background: Review credentials and education
    Visitor->>Contact: Choose approved contact method
```
### Optional Link Visibility ###

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant JS as script.js
    participant Config as Profile Config
    participant UI as Website UI

    JS->>Config: Read optional values
    alt CV link unavailable
        JS->>UI: Hide Download CV control
    else CV link available
        JS->>UI: Show Download CV control
    end
    alt LinkedIn unavailable
        JS->>UI: Hide LinkedIn link
    else LinkedIn available
        JS->>UI: Show LinkedIn link
    end
```

